  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And later on, he-- he came to-- to North Africa and I mean, and he was the one who-- who help him, Menachem Begin, when he was there in hiding, to escape.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, well, there-- I mean, we were very happy and it was a very-- you know, Rhodes Island was like a paradise.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, even now, after the war, they go plenty-- thousands and thousands of tourists because it's so beautiful.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So much so, you know, they made even a perfume in-- in France, which is called the [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Notte ?] de [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Rhodi, ?] in Italian means the-- the-- the nights of Rhodes because it's a smell, it's a perfume that you cannot describe, you know, only in the Orient.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As living, you know, there, and we can-- when you were at night, you know, in summer, especially, and you cannot-- you cannot even sleep, so much perfume, it was all over.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was a really very, very happy life we had.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Though we were not very rich, the majority, but everybody was happy because they make their living and they were happy and you could hear in the street, sing-- songs and everybody was singing and you know, they were very, very happy.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was my what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was seeing myself a doctor because I wanted to go to university and I want to study and I want to find some-- some like you say, some medicine, some cure for some diseases unknown.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, that's 50 years ago.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it was-- a woman, nowadays, they have discovered many things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at the time, it was many-- you know, even for a simple flu, there was nothing that you can have, not even an aspirin or whatever.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
